headline: Record First Half at ICE Bonds for Corporate and Municipal Bond Trading
summary: ATLANTA & NEW YORK, August 18, 2025--Intercontinental Exchange (NYSE: ICE), a leading global provider of technology and data, today announced record trading volume in the first half of 2025 for corporate bond and municipal bond trading on the ICE Bonds’ electronic execution platforms.
